edBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/28/fuNbCO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F28%2FfuNbCO.png&h=29f891eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3鏡頭與4鏡頭"},{"pid":"249f9db221336be8c5cb000138734799cb815913","tid":1267713,"uid":46511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:53:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>支援 5G、搭高通 S855，最新爆料指三星 Galaxy A90 將衝上旗艦等級</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nMason(recaro) 2019-06-26 10:38<br />\n      <br />\n三星先前重新改變旗下的手機產品設計政策，最新技術會先搭載到整併了 J、M 系列的全新 Galaxy A 系列當中；不過當前的 Galaxy A 系列最高階產品依然不脫中高階定位，雖然能嘗鮮新技術但規格還無法和 Note 以及 S 系列等旗艦機款相比。<br />\n<br />\n但根據最新的爆料，Galaxy A 系列主打中階、入門市場的情況將有所改變，三星打算讓 Galaxy A 系列的最高階產品 A90 衝上旗艦等級，不只將搭載高通 S855 處理器，甚至還將支援 5G 連線。<br />\n<br />\n支援 5G、搭高通 S855，最新爆料指三星 Galaxy A90 將衝上旗艦等級<br />\n<br />\n前陣子有傳聞指出三星 Galaxy A 系列將會有一款最高階的 A90，然後知名的爆料達人 @Onleaks 先前表示這款 A90 會以 Galaxy R 系列的身分推出。但不久前 @Onleaks 發文表示自己的線人搞錯了內部型號，其實 Galaxy A90 確實存在，然後 @Onleaks 為了「贖罪 」還加碼爆料了 Galaxy A90 的幾項關鍵規格。<br />\n<br />\n@Onleaks 指出三星 Galaxy A90 會有 SM-A908 以及 SM-A905 兩種不同款式，當中的 SM-A908 將搭載 6.7 吋螢幕並支援螢幕指紋辨識機能，還將搭配高通 S855 處理器、48MP+8MP+5MP 的三主鏡頭，而且還將支援 5G 連網機能。至於 SM-A905 也搭載 6.7 吋螢幕、支援螢幕指紋辨識機能、內建高通 S855 處理器，三主鏡頭則是 48MP+12MP+5MP 的組合，然後還會支援 Tilt OIS 移軸光學防手震機能。<br />\n<br />\n另外，先前還有額外的情報指出，三星 Galaxy A90 系列還將支援 45W 快充機能。<br />\n <br />\nIn order to somehow make amends, I bring you the key specs of these devices 😜<br />\n<br />\n- SM-A908: SD855, 6.7-inch screen with in-display FPS, 48+8+5 rear camera, 5G support.<br />\n- SM-A905: SD855, 6.7-inch screen with in-display FPS, 48+12+5 rear camera with exclusive Tilt OIS tech!<br />\n<br />\nCheers! <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/uqfFTnfoIQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FuqfFTnfoIQ&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGkUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=a6cb396d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/uqfFTnfoIQ</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash; Steve H.McFly (@OnLeaks) 2019年6月25日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然三星 Galaxy A90 系列的 SM-A908、SM-A905 兩款機型規格稍有差異，但產品定位已經衝破過往 A 系列的中高階而上到了旗艦等級；若相關情報內容都屬實的話，Galaxy A90 系列整體的規格吸引力甚至不輸給 Note 和 S 系列，但 Galaxy A90 何時會正式發表、價格將會如何定位目前都還未知。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4523/213410/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4523%2F213410%2F1%2F&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGkUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=9a1fa148\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4523/213410/1/</a>"},{"pid":"aefb08fe9130023ed44851e493899b43d12c9913","tid":1267713,"uid":36970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:05:13.000Z","msg":"曲mon?"},{"pid":"d59c7ef9bd9b7cb850aa98c8233c07516c4f5ba1","tid":1267713,"uid":46511,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"aefb08fe9130023ed44851e493899b43d12c9913","tid":1267713,"uid":36970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:05:13.000Z","msg":"曲mon?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:14:02.000Z","msg":"A系列邊會出曲moon㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608d9aa38eb8e71ac8e456b8da1818904fb72e78","tid":1267713,"uid":198355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:17:02.000Z","msg":"好唔好以細部d? 好難揸手"},{"pid":"976776fb486460bd05fd5f318dd603441b63bf06","tid":1267713,"uid":36970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"608d9aa38eb8e71ac8e456b8da1818904fb72e78","tid":1267713,"uid":198355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:17:02.000Z","msg":"好唔好以細部d? 好難揸手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:22:16.000Z","msg":"有A70"},{"pid":"1c51feba66760f2b53f70b2494ffab7c9beaeba7","tid":1267713,"uid":6860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:48:57.000Z","msg":"note 10又係同一cpu, spec咁似咁仲邊有人買"},{"pid":"7a79e1c1ee169b5f4adb641fb14261f465a23b2c","tid":1267713,"uid":164985,"lik